snippet.title: The All-Stars of Disney Sports Basketball
snippet.description: If you beat the Challenge Cup mode in Disney Sports Basketball you can unlock the All-Star Team Challenge. There are Four All-Star teams in all featuring all of the special characters in the game. Mickey's All-Stars, Donald's All-Stars, Goofy's All-Stars and Pete's All-Stars.
